<seg id="4"> Main: Wednesday 9 Muharram 1427 AH - February 8, 2006 CE, Islam Diary: </seg>
<seg id="5"> For Muslims to know the status of their Prophet Peace Be Upon Him... and for Muslims to know what real love for this great prophet is...these were the situations </seg>
