<seg id="18"> On the day Mecca was liberated, Abu Qahafa (the father of Abu Bakr) became a Muslim. He turned to Islam very late in life and was blind so Abu Bakr took him to see the Prophet (peace be upon him) so that he could declare his faith in Islam and pay homage to the Prophet (peace be upon him). </seg>
