<seg id="6"> In the course of his discussion about the possibilities that will be available in the future in the area of alternative energies, and in addition to more work for exploiting solar energy and wind energy, that nuclear energy is considered the most important alternative energy that can be exploited for the purpose of producing electricity, especially considering that the Tunisian electric grid is capable of absorbing and transporting the enormous electric power that nuclear energy can produce. </seg>
