<seg id="32"> And if this hesitation continues, the priority of Washington and its allies will once again be military security, not politics, </seg>
<seg id="33"> despite public declarations issued many times by President Bush Junior and both his former Secretary of State Colin Powell and current Secretary Rice, which attributed the main reason of the uprising of anti-Western anti-American terrorist groups to be their support, for the past 60 years, of the security option over freedom and democracy... </seg>
</p>
